{
  "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "两个向量之间，其实有两种完全不同的相乘方式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "一种叫点积，结果是一个数；另一种叫叉积，结果又是一个向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "别急，我们一个一个来看，它们背后都藏着清晰的几何图像。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "dot",
      "line_id": "dot-1",
      "filename": "dot-dot-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/dot-dot-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "点积的算法很简单：把两个向量对应的坐标相乘，再全部加起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "dot",
      "line_id": "dot-2",
      "filename": "dot-dot-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/dot-dot-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "它还等于两个向量的长度相乘，再乘以夹角的余弦。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "dot",
      "line_id": "dot-3",
      "filename": "dot-dot-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/dot-dot-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.44,
      "size": 39024,
      "text": "所以点积衡量的是：一个向量在另一个向量方向上投影了多少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "dot",
      "line_id": "dot-4",
      "filename": "dot-dot-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/dot-dot-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "当两个向量垂直时，投影为零，点积也就等于零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "cross",
      "line_id": "cross-1",
      "filename": "cross-cross-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/cross-cross-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "叉积则不一样，它得到的是一个全新的向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "cross",
      "line_id": "cross-2",
      "filename": "cross-cross-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/cross-cross-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "这个新向量的方向，同时垂直于原来的两个向量，用右手定则来判断。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "cross",
      "line_id": "cross-3",
      "filename": "cross-cross-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/cross-cross-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "它的长度，等于两个向量张成的平行四边形的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "geometry",
      "line_id": "geo-1",
      "filename": "geometry-geo-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/geometry-geo-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "点积用余弦，管的是投影和方向的接近程度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "geometry",
      "line_id": "geo-2",
      "filename": "geometry-geo-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/geometry-geo-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "叉积用正弦，管的是面积和方向的张开程度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "geometry",
      "line_id": "geo-3",
      "filename": "geometry-geo-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/geometry-geo-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "一个看平行，一个看垂直，它们恰好互补。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "拖动或切换向量，看看垂直时点积怎样归零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "再看平行时，平行四边形塌成一条线，叉积也随之归零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "点积是标量，用余弦，联系着投影与做功。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "叉积是向量，用正弦，联系着面积与力矩。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "dot-cross-product",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/dot-cross-product/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "两种乘法，两种视角，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 35.56,
  "total_size": 568944,
